 \"to\": 2759}, {\"ngram\": \"the bulk\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2818}, {\"ngram\": \"its budgets\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2833}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This means that, every day, the equivalent of $4.2 million goes to help athletes and sports organisations at all levels around the world,\\\" it said.\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 3029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the equivalent\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"sports organisations\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2987}, {\"ngram\": \"all levels\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 3001}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reaction from competitors has been mixed.\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reaction\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swedish pole vaulter Armand Duplantis, who plans to take part in the Paris games called it \\\"a good thing \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 considering at the last Olympics there was no prize money at all.\\\"\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3078, \"end\": 3085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999880639569018, \"rank\": 1.0268985360823832e-05, \"text\": \"Swedish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}, {\"begin\": 3099, \"end\": 3115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Armand Duplantis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\"}, {\"begin\": 3147, \"end\": 3152, \"title\":